{"tid":14792,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[傷心事]玩交友Apps識左個女仔","createTime":"2016-11-30T15:59:39.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-01T14:37:54.000Z","uid":3113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"13f73466eab6f8d02e8d1686ed593e8f883055b4","tid":14792,"uid":3113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T15:59:39.000Z","msg":"早排喺交友apps 識左個女仔出過幾次街都幾啱feel<br />\n最難忘有次佢仲有日我返工佢經過公司樓下買左杯咖啡俾我<br />\n<br />\n我成日都flirt佢而佢有時又有反應<br />\n直到有日出街手都拖埋但又唔肯做我女朋友住<br />\n又話太快<br />\n<br />\n第二日如常whatsapp吹下水無耐就已讀不回, 到而家已經足足兩個禮拜<br />\n<br />\n我認我今次認真左但最後只想放低幾句說話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : <br />\n對唔住其實我呃左你, 我唔係處<br />\n其實到底你諗緊咩, 明明有feel但又可以一言不發咁走左去..<br />\n雖然剛剛unfriend同unfollow 左你但唔知點解我仲有啲掛住你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n祝生活安好順利畢業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e066cb9ed9881f1adc5522b66cdbce2029eec6e","tid":14792,"uid":18667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T16:03:23.000Z","msg":"可能人地搵到個更好嘅呢<br />\n祝福人地啦"},{"pid":"2a8d7fac786c1b07b6caf0e6b06afbe6a1f7db67","tid":14792,"uid":36687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T16:10:54.000Z","msg":"女人如衣服"},{"pid":"1995342a4598fbd9012c569f68b871bcd56ba866","tid":14792,"uid":43297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T17:20:00.000Z","msg":"玩交友app就要有心理準備佢係魚翁，放開d啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95c460231ab744d52a557dc345b73c5ae65461c5","tid":14792,"uid":3113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T00:28:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>玩交友app就要有心理準備佢係魚翁，放開d啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n放開緊, 只係上黎放低幾句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"489770e11eefe44ed62f13f730cc0cadbe5f94db","tid":14792,"uid":33971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,